# arduino
 
 - [buy an arduino uno knockoff from amazon](https://www.amazon.com/ELEGOO-Board-ATmega328P-ATMEGA16U2-Compliant/dp/B01EWOE0UU/)
 - [Download and install the Arduino IDE](https://www.arduino.cc/en/software)
 - program the board with:
 - [pyramids.ino](https://github.com/LafeLabs/pibrary/blob/main/factory/pyramidscode/code/pyramids.ino)
 - put the [shield](scrolls/electronics) on(add photograph)
 - connect the sensor, or make sure it's already connected(photos)
 - powered with the [solar power plant](scrolls/solar)

